### ── Phase 4: Single-vehicle ask (existing, verify still works) ───────

### 4.1 Single vehicle ask - BMW M3
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the horsepower and 0-60 time?",
  "topK": 3
}

> {%
