### ── Phase 5: ParadeDB hybrid search ──────────────────────────────────

### 5.1 Hybrid search - balanced (0.7 vector, 0.3 BM25)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask/hybrid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "sports sedan with best track performance",
  "topK": 5,
  "vectorWeight": 0.7
}

> {%
    client.log("=== HYBRID RESULTS (0.7 vector) ===");
    response.body?.forEach(h => {
        client.log("  #" + h.rank + " " + h.vehicleId + " score=" + h.hybridScore?.toFixed(4) + " - " + h.excerpt?.substring(0, 80));
    });
%}

###

### 5.2 Hybrid search - keyword-heavy (0.3 vector, 0.7 BM25)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask/hybrid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "automatic emergency braking standard",
  "topK": 5,
  "vectorWeight": 0.3
}

> {%
    client.log("=== HYBRID RESULTS (0.3 vector) ===");
    response.body?.forEach(h => {
        client.log("  #" + h.rank + " " + h.vehicleId + " score=" + h.hybridScore?.toFixed(4));
    });
%}

###

### 5.3 Hybrid search - pure vector (1.0 vector, 0.0 BM25)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask/hybrid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "electric car with longest range",
  "topK": 5,
  "vectorWeight": 1.0
}

###

### 5.4 Hybrid search - pure BM25 (0.0 vector, 1.0 BM25)
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask/hybrid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "electric car with longest range",
  "topK": 5,
  "vectorWeight": 0.0
}

