### ── Phase 6: Existing fleet search (single-tier, backward compat) ────

### 6.1 Old fleet search - should still work
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Which vehicles have over 400 horsepower?",
  "topK": 5
}

> {%
    client.log("=== OLD FLEET (single-tier) ===");
    response.body?.forEach(h => {
