### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Checklist
### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###
### Phase 1-2: Ingestion + summaries
###   ✓ Batch embed: "Embedding batch 0-N of N texts"
###   ✓ Summary: "Vehicle summary upserted for..."
###   ✓ GET /vehicles/admin/summaries shows all vehicles
###
### Phase 3: Two-tier fleet search
###   ✓ tier1Ms and totalMs in response
###   ✓ candidates list shows vehicles ranked by relevance
###   ✓ results list shows detail chunks
###
### Phase 4: Single-vehicle (backward compat)
###   ✓ Works without two-tier
###
### Phase 5: ParadeDB hybrid
###   ✓ vectorWeight changes ranking
###   ✓ Pure vector and pure BM25 both work
###   ✓ If ParadeDB not set up, these return SQL errors (expected)
###
### Phase 6: Old fleet (backward compat)
###   ✓ POST /vehicles/ask still works
###
### Phase 7: Bulk ingestion
###   ✓ 3 vehicles ingested in one call
###   ✓ Summaries populated for all 3
###
### Phase 8: Multi-agent
###   ✓ Vehicle query → vehicle agent
###   ✓ Article query → article agent
